{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"ResizeObserver.observe()","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/ResizeObserver/observe","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Resize_Observer_API\">Resize Observer API <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ResizeObserver\"><code>ResizeObserver</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>コンストラクター</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ResizeObserver/ResizeObserver\"><code>ResizeObserver()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ResizeObserver/disconnect\"><code>disconnect()</code></a></li><li><em><code>observe()</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ResizeObserver/unobserve\"><code>unobserve()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Resize Observer API に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ResizeObserverEntry\"><code>ResizeObserverEntry</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong><code>observe()</code></strong> は <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ResizeObserver\"><code>ResizeObserver</code></a> インターフェイスのメソッドで、指定された <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a> または <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SVGElement\"><code>SVGElement</code></a> の監視を開始します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"構文","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token function\">observe</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">observe</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> options<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"引数","title":"引数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"target\"><code>target</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>監視する <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a> または <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SVGElement\"><code>SVGElement</code></a> への参照。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"options\"><code>options</code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">省略可</span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>監視のオプションを設定することができるオプションオブジェクトです。現在、設定可能なオプションは 1 つだけです。</p>\n    <dl>\n      <dt id=\"box\"><code>box</code></dt>\n      <dd>\n        <p>オブザーバーがどのボックスモデルの変更を観察するかを設定します。設定可能な値は以下の通りです。</p>\n        <dl>\n          <dt id=\"content-box\"><code>content-box</code> (既定値)</dt>\n          <dd>\n            <p>CSS　で定義されたコンテンツ領域のサイズ。</p>\n          </dd>\n          <dt id=\"border-box\"><code>border-box</code></dt>\n          <dd>\n            <p>CSS で定義されたボックス境界領域のサイズ。</p>\n          </dd>\n          <dt id=\"device-pixel-content-box\"><code>device-pixel-content-box</code></dt>\n          <dd>\n            <p>CSS で定義されたコンテンツ領域の大きさ。デバイスピクセル単位で、要素またはその祖先に対して CSS 変換を適用する前の値。</p>\n          </dd>\n        </dl>\n      </dd>\n    </dl>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"返値","title":"返値","isH3":true,"content":"<p>なし (<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/undefined\"><code>undefined</code></a>)。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例外","title":"例外","isH3":true,"content":"<p>なし。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>次のスニペットは <a href=\"https://mdn.github.io/dom-examples/resize-observer/resize-observer-text.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">resize-observer-text.html</a> (<a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/dom-examples/blob/master/resize-observer/resize-observer-text.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ソースを表示</a>) の例から取ったものです。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> resizeObserver <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ResizeObserver</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">entries</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> entry <span class=\"token keyword\">of</span> entries<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>entry<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>contentBoxSize<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token comment\">// クロームが標準外の配列を使用しているかどうかのチェック</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>entry<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>contentBoxSize<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        h1Elem<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>style<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>fontSize <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Math<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">max</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1.5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> entry<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>contentBoxSize<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>inlineSize<span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token number\">200</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">'rem'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        pElem<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>style<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>fontSize <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Math<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">max</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> entry<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>contentBoxSize<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>inlineSize<span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token number\">600</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">'rem'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        h1Elem<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>style<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>fontSize <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Math<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">max</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1.5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> entry<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>contentBoxSize<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>inlineSize<span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token number\">200</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">'rem'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        pElem<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>style<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>fontSize <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Math<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">max</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> entry<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>contentBoxSize<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>inlineSize<span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token number\">600</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">'rem'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      h1Elem<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>style<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>fontSize <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Math<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">max</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1.5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> entry<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>contentRect<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>width<span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token number\">200</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">'rem'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      pElem<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>style<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>fontSize <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Math<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">max</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> entry<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>contentRect<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>width<span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token number\">600</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">'rem'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Size changed'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nresizeObserver<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">observe</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>divElem<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>オプションオブジェクトを使った <code>observe()</code> の呼び出しは、次のようになります。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>resizeObserver<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">observe</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>divElem<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">box</span> <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'border-box'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"仕様書","id":"仕様書","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://drafts.csswg.org/resize-observer/#dom-resizeobserver-observe","title":"Resize Observer"}],"query":"api.ResizeObserver.observe"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"ブラウザーの互換性","isH3":false,"query":"api.ResizeObserver.observe","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/ResizeObserver/observe/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"構文"},{"text":"例","id":"例"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"仕様書"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"ブラウザーの互換性"}],"summary":"observe() は ResizeObserver インターフェイスのメソッドで、指定された Element または SVGElement の監視を開始します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"ResizeObserver.observe()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"ResizeObserver.observe()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/resizeobserver/observe","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/resizeobserver/observe/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/ResizeObserver","title":"ResizeObserver"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/ResizeObserver/observe","title":"ResizeObserver.observe()"}],"pageTitle":"ResizeObserver.observe() - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}